  "title": "AB03 - Telemarketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Telemarketer</strong></p><p>Working hours: Mon – Fri, 10am – 6pm<br />Location: Work from home (WFH)<br />Salary: $1800 - $2200 + Commission</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct outbound telemarketing calls for banking-related products and services</li><li>Introduce and explain banking products clearly and professionally</li><li>Identify customer needs and qualify potential leads</li><li>Set appointments or refer interested customers to relationship managers / sales team</li><li>Follow up with warm leads when required</li><li>Maintain accurate records of calls, responses, and outcomes</li><li>Achieve daily and monthly call and lead targets</li><li>Comply with company policies and basic banking compliance guidelines</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Min 1 year of relevant experience</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
